## callUp

呼起本地客户端

### Parameters

-   `options` **[object][1]** 

### Examples

```javascript
callUp({
	startTime: Date.now(),
	waiting: 800,
	waitingLimit: 50,
	protocol : scheme,
	fallbackUrl : download,
	onFallback : function() {
		// should download
	}
});
```

[1]: https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object
